    Slice numbers   rupture.scale
    1               0
    2               480px
    3               580px
    4               680px
    5               780px
    6               880px
    7               980px
    8               1080px
    9               1180px
    10              1280px
    11              1380px
    12              1480px
    13              1580px
    14              1680px
    15              1780px
    16              1880px
*/
